&lt;h1&gt;Project Support Officer&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and self-motivated Project Support Officer with a can-do attitude and excellent communication skills to join our Service and System Transformation Team at the West of England Academic Health Science Network.&lt;br /&gt;Relevant experience would be an advantage, but we’re equally interested in finding a kind and helpful candidate to join our experienced and established team. You will need to be super organised and able to work across a range of projects and priorities at the same time, and able to be proactive.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you would like to find out more about this opportunity or to arrange an informal discussion, please contact Nathalie Delaney, Programme Manager by email Nathalie.delaney@weahsn.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shortlisted candidates will be notified by 19 November 2020 and interviews will take place in the week of the 23 November.&lt;/p&gt;
